Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previous on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus started the Battle of Fairy Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a fierce struggle against rune \Ntraps and the Raijin Tribe. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the only people left are Natsu and \NGajeel who, for some reason, can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Erza's back, and Mystogan \Narrived in town as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although {\i1}I'm{\i0} still stoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} good, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would challenge me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I defeat you, then everyone \Nwill return to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had an artificial eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... Fairy Machine Gun Leprechaun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:58.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can actually defend \Nagainst this many needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder how you'll handle twice as many!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For today henceforth, {\i1}I{\i0} \Nwill be known as Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For I am the true Fairy Queen! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like you\Nis still a fellow Fairy Tail wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to call yourself \NTitania, then feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know who gave me that \Nnickname in the first place anyway. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:57.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cease this foolishness and return \Neveryone to normal, I will not harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being a bit naive here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Stone Eyes have another power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remote control. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bow down before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not, I can turn those stone \Nwomen into piles of rubble from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you value victory over your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very admirable of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:42.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will purify the souls of those \Nturned to dust with your very life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's how you bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:18.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza vs. Evergreen. Winner: Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hostages have been freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what will you do, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could Eve lose to the likes of Erza? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you get so weak, Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a job for Bickslow or myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you returned, Freed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hostages freed, the \Nmaster will no longer budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't follow me, then get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't needed in my Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle of Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With you all returned to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way I'm going to play\NLaxus's silly game any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what about everyone that was \Ninjured from Freed's traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't teach Laxus a \Nlesson, he'll never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him a punishment \Nhe'll never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to get \Naway with it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to agree with Laxus about the whole \Ndeciding who the strongest in Fairy Tail is thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't be so hard on the guy, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway... The second Battle \Nof Fairy Tail starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we haven't done anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying it like you're \Nserious or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, I'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, don't encourage him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... I don't think fighting \Nwomen really counts as a battle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, woman... Doesn't matter to me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that face is pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Lucy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Gajeel-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guild sure is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a screw loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something happening again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we'll be your opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems one of the rules is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll make a new rule now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for the Battle of Fairy Tail to \Ncontinue, I have activated the Thunder Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have one hour and ten minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you retire, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on getting innocent \Npeople involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get his usual medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Thunder Palace thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone look outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt lacrima... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those things doing up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows. Must be those Fairy \NTail guys up to something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure wish they'd cut it out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be preparing fireworks \Nfor the Harvest Festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I bet you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe those Fairy Tail guys are \Nactually on the ball for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're floating above the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of those lacrima stores a great \Ndeal of magical thunder energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this Thunder Palace is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the Thunder Palace means, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Magnolia is the target...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happens if those things discharge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless thunderbolts will \Nrain down on the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper Rifle Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Target: Lock on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stinger Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess they aren't fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Bisca.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get 'em all like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that because of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they might be dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there, Bisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Body Link Magic. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Body Link Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those lacrima are under a spell linked\Nback to the one who destroys them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,inflicting equal damage to what they received. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:26.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words if you attack them, that \Nsame damage gets sent back to you.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the people in the city will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to beat Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try and get the people \Nof the city to evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still two of the Raijin Tribe left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:18.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's gonna make \Na scene again, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My next hostages are everyone \Nin the entire city!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that bastard thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll decide what's "too far."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be master so bad, \Nthen fight Gramps yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fight to the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until one of us is wiped \Nout, this battle won't end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another invisible wall here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:19.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the writing magics, \Nso I might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Levy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you two can stop Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:44.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take the information from the \Narrangement of the rouge letters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and break it down to the letter materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pick up the vocabulary \Nused to construct the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L, O, S, U...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, changing it further to Gheel grammar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:59.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely no idea \Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:13:59.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L and S are bluffs! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The key-code is Als! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you guys out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be doing something! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thunder Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go that far, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Freed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bickslow is still out \Nhunting Fairies, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the old man's best hope, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You get Cana and that woman from Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need either of them in my Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're our enemies \Nnow, we're still in the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:03.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I gave you an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the path we've taken, \Nthere's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow you, even to the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accomplish my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No more pulled punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have regrets, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That will do, Darkness Freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to show me your true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Evergreen, Laxus \Nis here in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the men's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we win a prize or something? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lax...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other place \Nyou think Laxus could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have known him a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:31.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I guess you could say \Nhe's lost any perspective he had... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you use the guild's loudspeakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The runes said that during the Battle of \NFairy Tail only the master could use it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They really did think of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have to get the people of the \Ncity to evacuate away from the Thunder Palace! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:52.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I think it might be better not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:59.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of people from outside \NMagnolia here for the Harvest Festival right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's in chaos already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:04.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the people are looking \Nup uneasily at those lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:10.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, that's why if you tell them what \Nthey are, you're sure to cause a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ton of people will get injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:26.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's at it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bickslow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the newbie I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard what about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I even want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hot-headed princess who \Nloves cosplay and meat! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who comes up with these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this? A cheerleader?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, babies... Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally I'd go easy 'cause you're new,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we got this game going on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think the master \Nwill forgive you for doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need the master's forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:22.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because when this game is over, \NLaxus will be the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those flying things are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Archer, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call? Moshimoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it's Celestial Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your Spirit's into cosplay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for those flying things, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that, as it were! Moshimoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First you're frozen, and now you're dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As it were! Moshimoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... My babies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to surrender, now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Babies... Babies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Babies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psych!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshimoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:25.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take a short break...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hobby shop under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a treasure trove of dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:39.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many dolls you destroy, it \Ndoes nothing to me, a manipulator of souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:45.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bickslow uses magic that lets \Nhim possess dolls with souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't retreat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout this, cosplay girly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Offer your soul to Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Baryon Formation! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like only I can go through the \Ngate freely regardless of your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:45.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that our love has shattered the \Nbarrier between man and spirit, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come to keep \Nmy promise, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke! So you {\i1}were{\i0} a Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I never told anybody your \Nsecret, and now you turn on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can see people's souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining in for the Battle of Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care that \Nmuch about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just won't allow you to harm \Nmy owner, Lucy, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not allow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:33.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, you've never beaten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was always holding \Nback when we fought! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rough 'im up like the old times, my babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits aren't shields. I fight \Nalongside them! That's my style!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You llllike him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about the dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's an opening, you \Ngo after Bickslow, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regulus, grant me power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:33.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:43.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,we even kindly overlooked the little lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:58.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll protect that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:03.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:10.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:15.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,all my happiness and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:23.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:30.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it like we've just been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:36.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like flowers blown in a summer wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:44.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,let us bloom brightly in this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you destroyed the request board again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better hurry and \Napologize to Mira, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't be stupid, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize what'll happen \Nif Mira gets angry for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get away with only 2 or \N3 broken ribs, I just know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:12.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every bone in my entire body, one at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:13.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, snap?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Satan's Decent
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'm stronger than she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then I'll go tell Mira, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go get some fish instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
